1 0 0 1 54 332 Tm (? Feel specific to the product and shopper context.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 318 Tm (? Surface the most likely objection or next step.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 304 Tm (? Increase add-to-cart rate from PDP conversations.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 290 Tm (? Increase productive follow-up interactions.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 276 Tm (? Reduce generic "browse more" behavior when a better contextual action exists.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 248 Tm (Non-Goals) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 234 Tm (? Rebuilding the overall chat architecture.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 220 Tm (? Generating free-form NBA copy with an LLM at runtime.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 206 Tm (? Replacing the full PDP card or checkout logic.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 192 Tm (? Solving personalization beyond session-level context in v1.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 164 Tm (Design Principles) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 150 Tm (1. Be contextual, not generic.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 136 Tm (   Chips should reflect the product type, product attributes, session intent,) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 122 Tm (   and shopper stage.) Tj
1 0 0 1 54 94 Tm (2. Resolve friction before expanding choice.) Tj
